graph TB
    subgraph "CodeFlare Operator Pod"
        Controller[Controller Manager]
        RayController[RayCluster Controller]
        AppWrapperController[AppWrapper Controller<br/>conditionally enabled]
        MutatingWebhook[Mutating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        ValidatingWebhook[Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        CertController[Cert Controller]
        MetricsServer[Metrics Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        HealthServer[Health Server<br/>8081/TCP HTTP]

        Controller --> RayController
        Controller --> AppWrapperController
        Controller --> MutatingWebhook
        Controller --> ValidatingWebhook
        Controller --> CertController
        Controller --> MetricsServer
        Controller --> HealthServer
    end

    subgraph "CRDs Watched"
        RayClusterCR[RayCluster<br/>ray.io/v1<br/>from KubeRay]
        AppWrapperCR[AppWrapper<br/>workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta2]
        DSCInit[DSCInitialization<br/>dscinitialization.opendatahub.io]
    end

    subgraph "Resources Created per RayCluster"
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>OpenShift only]
        NetworkPolicies[NetworkPolicies<br/>head & worker isolation]
        Routes[Routes/Ingress<br/>dashboard & client]
        Secrets[Secrets<br/>OAuth, TLS, CA certs]
        Services[Services<br/>oauth-proxy, head-svc]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.1.0+]
        Kueue[Kueue<br/>v0.8.3<br/>conditional]
        CertManager[cert-controller<br/>v0.10.1]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>optional]
    end

    subgraph "ODH/RHOAI Integration"
        ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator<br/>DSCInitialization]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>openshift-monitoring]
    end

    User[User] -->|creates| RayClusterCR
    User -->|creates| AppWrapperCR

    RayClusterCR -->|watched by| RayController
    AppWrapperCR -->|watched by| AppWrapperController
    DSCInit -->|read by| Controller

    RayController -->|creates/manages| OAuthProxy
    RayController -->|creates| NetworkPolicies
    RayController -->|creates| Routes
    RayController -->|creates| Secrets
    RayController -->|creates| Services

    MutatingWebhook -->|mutates on CREATE| RayClusterCR
    MutatingWebhook -->|mutates on CREATE| AppWrapperCR
    ValidatingWebhook -->|validates CREATE/UPDATE| RayClusterCR
    ValidatingWebhook -->|validates CREATE/UPDATE| AppWrapperCR

    Controller -->|coordinates with| KubeRay
    AppWrapperController -->|creates Workload CRs| Kueue
    CertController -->|uses| CertManager
    Controller -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OpenShiftOAuth

    Controller -->|reads| ODHOperator
    MetricsServer -->|scraped by| Prometheus

